    "en": {
      "title": "Important announcement regarding power cuts tomorrow",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Public Utilities Commission has informed that power cut will be implemented in the country tomorrow for 3 hours and 40 minutes.",
        "Accordingly, power cut will be enforced for 2 hours 20 minutes during day and 1 hour 20 minutes at night in sections ABCDEFGHIJKLPQRSTUVW.",
        "It is noteworthy that the Public Utilities Commission of Sri Lanka has also informed that there will be a power cut for 2 hours and 30 minutes in Athudu CC section from 6.00 am to 8.30 am and 3 hours blackout will be implemented in MNOXYZ sections from 5.30 am to 8.30 am."
      ],
